<plot>How did Oceanic 815 crash on the mysterious island of LOST? More importantly, what is the fate of its survivors? LOST Executive Producers Damon Lindelof and Carlton Cuse explore the answers to those questions and many more in an in depth look at the past, present and future of one of the most talked-about shows on television. Don't miss LOST:The Answers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?343921</url></doc>
